      <text>Task A — Celsius to Fahrenheit</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>Write a function <code>celsius_to_fahrenheit(celsius)</code> that takes a temperature in Celsius and returns the equivalent temperature in Fahrenheit.</p>
<p>The conversion formula is: F = C &times; 1.8 + 32</p>]]></text>
