    <answer>def celsius_to_fahrenheit(celsius):
    """Convert a Celsius temperature to Fahrenheit."""
    SCALE_FACTOR = 1.8
    OFFSET = 32
    return celsius * SCALE_FACTOR + OFFSET</answer>
